                            <comment id="476955" author="adilger" created="Sat, 1 Nov 2025 16:44:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hongchao, can you please finish off this patch. I think it makes more sense to use CAP_SYS_RESOURCE for setting quota limits, since with that capability you could override the quota limits annyway, instead of CAP_SYS_ADMIN.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
